Package io.microraft.model.impl.log

Class DefaultLogEntryOrBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.microraft.model.impl.log.DefaultAbstractLogEntry
      • io.microraft.model.impl.log.DefaultLogEntryOrBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseLogEntry, LogEntry, LogEntry.LogEntryBuilder, RaftModel, Serializable
    public class DefaultLogEntryOrBuilder
extends DefaultAbstractLogEntry
implements LogEntry, LogEntry.LogEntryBuilder
    The default impl of the LogEntry and LogEntry.LogEntryBuilder interfaces. When an instance of this class is created, it is in the builder mode and its state is populated. Once all fields are set, the object switches to the DTO mode where it no longer allows mutations.

    Please note that build() does not verify if all fields are set or not. It is up to the user to populate the DTO state via the builder.
